<L>They wou'd be Gods, and be with <HI>Incense</HI> sought;</L>
<L>But 'tis a truth, fix't in the <HI>standard Rules,</HI></L>
<L>Your <HI>wou'd-be-wits</HI> are but the <HI>Van of Fools.</HI></L>
