<L>And will not see through the <HI>Transparent Cheat.</HI></L>
<L><HI>Pride</HI> is a Sin too obvious to conceal,</L>
<L>It puffs the Heart as Butchers do their Veal;</L>
<L>Looks fair without, but probe the hidden <HI>Mind,</HI></L>
<L>The Imposthume breaks and mixes with the wind.</L>
