<L>It is a wonder he cou'd live so long.</L>
<L>A <HI>Third</HI> you'l see sit whining for his <HI>Wife,</HI></L>
<L>His Earthly Heav'n and Comfort of his Life;&mdash;</L>
<L>Yet <HI>living,</HI> she ne'r fail'd to give him <HI>strife.</HI></L>
